			<h2 class="body-current-exhibit">About the gallery:</h2>

			<p class="body-copy light grey">Housed in a former 1930&rsquo;s service station, Ovvio Arte opened it&rsquo;s doors in 2007 as a setting where all art forms could converge and be explored. Under the direction of multi-disciplinary artists Veta Cicolello and Theo Antoniadis, Ovvio has produced award winning performance art, visual art exhibitions, and music events featuring local and national artists. As a working studio, Ovvio has also been home base for the film, photography and fine art work of Veta&amp;Theo.</p>

